description:
#PickASide cause it honestly doesn’t matter, why? It’s designed that way. It’s designed to have you fighting pointlessly, I can lay out a laundromat of things each side has done to litterally destroy us. If you honestly in your heart think your political party has YOUR best interest you need to quit hitting snooze on your alarm. It’s disgusting what is going on and who’s controlling each party. No swamp drained, the #nationaldebt is spinning out of control and at the end of the day all of those people we vote in do absolutely nothing but talk a good game and play nice with their puppeteers! I know I have a lot of politically influenced people on here, and I respect what you post, you’re all really good people and want the best for our country and world, but I encourage you to dive deep into who and what is controlling them, who we fund and who’s really calling the shots 🧠💡 someone should really #draintheswamp #factsmatter #takebackamerica .
